description:
This EQ & Compression Course Will Help You Understand How To EQ From A Pro Audio Engineer Stand Point. You Will Also Understand How To Compress With A Few Stock Compressor Plug-In. In The Protools Session We Will Work On A Drum Loops And Also A Few Synth Lead Tracks. We Also Will Go Over Parallel Compression.

: Everything In The Video Course

: Over 45Mins Of Video

: Six Videos

:Three Videos On EQ

:Three Videos On Compression

: Also A Thank You Video


I Really Think This Course Can Help New And Old Engineers . Come Learn New Tips And

Tricks. This Course Will Help Your Workflow On All Levels.....
title: Avid Pro Tools 10 Basic EQ & Compression
